{"id": 2795, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都有哪些“秒回焦虑症”？", "description": "为了“秒回”这件事，你都跟自己或别人较过哪些劲？（题图来自：iStock ©️ logolis）", "record_count": 13708, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190218172000ha6I3jS8DBGoMdRr.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-02-25T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5407, "title": "你都有哪些“秒回焦虑症”？", "content": "你都有哪些“秒回焦虑症”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 328096, "content": "有时就算有空，也要刻意等一会儿再回", "image": "img/option/option/20190218235508sv5RGSxCDq4Ig9QJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 328097, "content": "对方一直不回就删掉对话框，假装没这回事", "image": "img/option/option/20190218235823N70ahrpoqFQuV3dg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 328098, "content": "聊到一半对方不回，就强行发一个“拜拜”过去", "image": "img/option/option/20190218235555nJ39dqh4QIw7TSWV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 328099, "content": "如果对方“已阅不回”，会觉得还不如“直接没看到”", "image": "img/option/option/20190218235947JW9Zh8LFpMXeKGSj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 328100, "content": "有时候会反向操作，自己故意不回", "image": "img/option/option/20190219000011n4OmKWiZa7cEbHtu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 328101, "content": "如果对方很久才回复，自己就要拖更久再回 ta", "image": "img/option/option/20190219000311zS86nirXMIlFWNkx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 328102, "content": "如果对方秒回，会有一种“ta 好像很闲”的错觉", "image": "img/option/option/20190219000046L1fFjzUPabexq5TC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 328103, "content": "会出现“想等等再认真回复，结果彻底忘记了”的状况", "image": "img/option/option/20190219000032iItT6C8d1M2NQzxw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 328104, "content": "都不会，我没有这些困扰", "image": "img/option/option/201902190000211Hc8FDafNgQq6dZe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}